## Components

### Buttons

| Variant | Background | Text | Border | Use |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Primary | `{{primary hex}}` | `{{snow}}` | none | {{Main CTA}} |
| Secondary | transparent | `{{primary}}` | `1px {{primary}}` | {{Secondary actions}} |
| Tertiary | transparent | `{{primary}}` | none | {{Minor links}} |
| Destructive | `{{error}}` | `{{snow}}` | none | {{Destructive actions, with confirmation}} |
| Disabled | `{{neutral-light}}` | `{{neutral-mid}}` | none | {{Loading / inactive}} |

States: hover (lighten/darken by {{X%}}), focus (ring `{{2px primary}}` offset {{2px}}), active (shift by {{1px}}), disabled (above).

