## Accessibility on web

- WCAG 2.1 AA minimum
- Focus visible (no `outline: none` without replacement)
- Skip-to-content link on every page
- Forms: labels associated, errors announced
- Headings: proper hierarchy (one h1 per page)
- Color: never the only signal

